title: O'NEILL PSYCHO 2 2011/12
description: The Psycho 2 known for warmth, flexibility and superior fit continues to evolve. We've upgraded to our all New Super Stretch XXXDS Neoprene. Along with the XDS-Air Firewall in the Chest and back, combined with Double Fluid Seam Weld to keep you warm and loose. The latest from Area 52 continues to be an industry leader and keeps you performing at the top of your game.
